(10445, 'Sildava 100mg 12 f.c. tab.', 'سيلدافا 100مجم 12 قرص', '91.5', '144', 'Sildenafil', 'Mash premiere', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
